headline: Nasdaq Halts Magnitude International Ltd
summary: NEW YORK, Dec. 19, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- The Nasdaq Stock Market® (Nasdaq: NDAQ) announced that trading is halted in Magnitude International Ltd (Nasdaq: MAGH) for additional information requested from the company. Previously, the Securities and Exchange Commission effected a trading suspension in MAGH from 04:00:00 on December 5, 2025 to 23:59:00 on December 18, 2025. The last sale price of the company’s shares was $6.76. More information about the SEC’s order can be found at https://www.sec
